er Road]]|location=[[Edinburgh]]|result=L}}\n\n=== League Cup ===\nOn 28 May 2019, Inverness were drawn into Group D of the [[2019\u201320 Scottish League Cup|Scottish League Cup]], alongside [[Dundee F.C.|Dundee]], [[Raith Rovers F.C.|Raith Rovers]], [[Peterhead F.C.|Peterhead]] and [[Cove Rangers F.C.|Cove Rangers]].\n\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date      =16 July 2019\n|time      =19:45\n|team1     =[[Peterhead F.C.|Peterhead]]\n|score     =0 \u2013 0\n|team2     =[[Inverness Caledonian Thistle F.C.|Inverness Caledonian Thistle]]\n|report    =https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/48994091\n|goals1    =\n|goals2    =\n|stadium   =[[Balmoor Stadium]]\n|location  =[[Peterhead]]\n|attendance=606\n|referee   =\n|id=|round=|penaltyscore=11 \u2013 10|result=L|penalties1={{pengoal}} [[Rory McAllister (footballer)|McAllister]]\n{{pengoal}} [[Billy Gibson (footballer, born 1990)|Gibson]]\n{{pengoal}} [[Jack Leitch|Leitch]]\n{{pengoal}}[[Jamie Stevenson (Scottish footballer)|Stevenson]]\n{{pengoal}} [[Ben Armour|Armour]]\n{{pengoal}} [[Patrick Boyle (footballer)|Boyle]]\n{{pengoal}} [[Jason Brown (footballer)|Brown]]\n{{pengoal}} [[Michael Dunlop|Dunlop]]\n{{pengoal}} [[Cameron Eadie|Eadie]]\n{{pengoal}} [[Simon Ferry|Ferry]]\n{{pengoal}} [[Greg Fleming|Fleming]]|penalties2={{pengoal}} [[Jordan White (footballer)|White]] \n{{pengoal}} [[Coll Donaldson|Donaldson]]\n{{pengoal}} [[Nikolay Todorov (footballer, born 1996)|Todorov]]\n{{pengoal}} [[Tom Walsh (footballer)|Walsh]]\n{{pengoal}} [[Carl Tremarco|Tremarco]]\n{{pengoal}} [[David Carson (footballer)|Carson]]\n{{pengoal}} [[Charlie Trafford|Trafford]]\n{{pengoal}} [[Jamie McCart|McCart]]\n{{pengoal}} [[Roddy MacGregor|MacGregor]]\n{{penmiss}} [[Mark Ridgers|Ridgers]]}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date      =20 July 2019\n|time      =15:00\n|team1     =[[Inverness Caledonian Thistle F.C.|Inverness Caledonian Thistle]]\n|score     =4 \u2013 1\n|team2     =[[Raith Rovers F.C.|Raith Rovers]]\n|report    =\n|goals1    =[[Jord