on Waltzer\n| colspan=\"8\" style=\"background:#ececec; text-align:center;\"|\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"1\" {{n/a|}}\n|-\n| [[Hugh Dancy]]\n| Caleb Garin\n| colspan=\"10\" style=\"background:#ececec; text-align:center;\"|\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n|-\n! colspan=\"12\" style=\"background-color:#ddf;\" | Police\n|-\n| [[James Carpinello]]\n| Anthony Burton\n| colspan=\"1\" {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"9\" {{n/a|}}\n|-\n| [[James McDaniel]]\n| Lou Johnson\n| colspan=\"1\" {{CGuest|Guest}}\n| colspan=\"3\" {{n/a|}}\n| colspan=\"1\" {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"5\" {{n/a|}}\n|-\n| [[Felix Solis]]\n| Kevin Rodriguez\n| colspan=\"1\" {{CGuest|Guest}}\n| colspan=\"1\" {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{n/a|}}\n| colspan=\"3\" {{CGuest|Guest}}\n| colspan=\"3\" {{n/a|}}\n|-\n| [[Jordana Spiro]]\n| Jenna Villette\n| colspan=\"4\" {{n/a|}}\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"5\" {{n/a|}}\n|-\n| [[John Ventimiglia]]\n| Gary Prima\n| colspan=\"5\" {{n/a|}}\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"4\" {{n/a|}}\n|-\n| Wendell B. Franklin\n| Capt. Ian Lawrence\n| colspan=\"8\" {{n/a|}}\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| {{CGuest|Guest}}\n|-\n! colspan=\"12\" style=\"background-color:#ddf;\" | Intelligence Agencies\n|-\n| [[Jill Flint]]\n| Lana Delaney\n| colspan=\"1\" {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"1\" {{CGuest|Guest}}\n| colspan=\"2\" {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"1\" {{n/a|}}\n| colspan=\"1\" {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"4\" {{n/a|}}\n|-\n| [[Kyle MacLachlan]]\n| AUSA Josh Perotti\n| colspan=\"3\" style=\"background:#ececec; text-align:center;\"|\n| colspan=\"1\" {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"1\" style=\"background:#ececec; text-align:center;\"|\n| colspan=\"1\" {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:#ececec; text-align:center;\"|\n|-\n| [[Eric Bogosian]]\n| Nelson Dubeck\n| colspan=\"4\" style=\"background:#ececec; text-align:center;\"|\n| {{CRecurring|Recurring}}\n| colspan=\"5\" 